title: My year in review is broken.

embed.description: Here are all my game stats proving how much I crushed it in the 2017 season.

body: When I share my page to twitter it comes out as someone else's information.

replies.body: I've been seeing a lot of these reports that the year in review website isn't working correctly in the client or on the website. It doesn't seem like we've gotten any info on what's going wrong, but try [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or using a different browser to see if that helps.

> [{quoted}](name=Broporo,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=EZl20iN2,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2017-12-19T21:43:58.935+0000)

It doesn't seem like we've gotten any info on what's going wrong, but try [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or using a different browser to see if that helps.
